@startuml
hide footbox
actor 仓管员
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "StockInOrderController" as Controller
participant "StockInOrderServiceImpl" as Service
database "MySQL数据库" as DB

仓管员 -> Frontend: 扫描入库单二维码
Frontend -> Controller: GET /stock/inOrder/m/{orderNo}
Controller -> Service: selectStockInOrderByOrderNo(orderNo)
Service -> DB: 查询入库单及明细
DB --> Service: 返回入库单数据
Service --> Controller: 返回入库单对象
Controller --> Frontend: 返回入库单及明细列表

Frontend -> Frontend: 显示入库明细

group 扫描物料标签
  仓管员 -> Frontend: 扫描标签，匹配明细
  Frontend -> Frontend: 累加扫码数量
end

仓管员 -> Frontend: 确认提交
Frontend -> Controller: POST /stock/inOrder/submitStockIn
Controller -> Service: submitStockIn(username, inOrder)

group 事务处理每条入库明细
  Service -> DB: 更新入库明细已入库数量
  Service -> DB: 更新库存（累加或新增）
  Service -> DB: 插入库存流水记录
end

Service -> DB: 更新入库单状态为已入库
Service --> Controller: 返回操作结果
Controller --> Frontend: 返回成功响应
Frontend --> 仓管员: 入库完成

@enduml